sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER , SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER , SEMESTERalias0.YEAR , STUDENT_RECORDalias0.GRADE FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 , STUDENT_RECORD AS STUDENT_RECORDalias0 WHERE STUDENT_ID = 1 AND STUDENT_RECORDalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID AND STUDENT_RECORDalias0.SEMESTER = SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID ;
